```
public static boolean find3Numbers(int arr[], int n, int X){
    Arrays.sort(arr);
    for (int i = 1; i &lt; n - 1; i++) { // from the second to penultimate
        int l = 0; // first index
        int r = n - 1; // last index
        while (l &lt; i &amp;&amp; r &gt; i) {
            int sum = arr[l] + arr[r] + arr[i];
            if (sum == X)
                return true;
            if (X &gt; sum)
                l++;
            else
                r--;
        }
    }
    return false;
}
```
 - time complexity - O(n^2) 
 - space complexity - O(1)

